ZH: 这场疾病会导致患者的肌肉萎缩。
EN: This disease can cause muscle atrophy in patients.

ZH: 长时间不使用肌肉会导致其萎缩。
EN: Prolonged inactivity of muscles can result in their atrophy.

ZH: 年老体弱的人常常会出现肌肉萎缩的问题。
EN: Elderly and frail individuals often experience muscle wastage.

ZH: 花费太多时间坐着会导致臀部肌肉萎缩。
EN: Spending too much time sitting can lead to the atrophy of buttock muscles.

ZH: 这条腿的肌肉萎缩得非常明显。
EN: The atrophy of the muscles in this leg is very pronounced.

ZH: 他的肌肉组织由于缺乏锻炼而萎缩。
EN: His muscle tissue has shrunk due to lack of exercise.

ZH: 这种疾病会导致心脏组织的萎缩。
EN: This disease can cause atrophy of heart tissue.

ZH: 缺乏充足的营养会使肌肉组织萎缩。
EN: Insufficient nutrition can result in muscle tissue atrophy.

ZH: 她的运动能力减弱是因为肌肉组织萎缩。
EN: Her reduced mobility is due to muscle tissue atrophy.

ZH: 营养不良会导致人体各处的器官萎缩。
EN: Malnutrition can lead to the atrophy of organs throughout the body.

ZH: 缺乏刺激会导致大脑功能萎缩。
EN: Lack of stimulation can result in the shrinking of brain function.

ZH: 这种草已经因干旱而开始萎缩。
EN: This grass has begun to wilt due to drought.

ZH: 高温天气会导致植物的叶子萎缩。
EN: Hot weather can cause the leaves of plants to shrivel.

ZH: 水分不足会使植物的根部萎缩。
EN: Insufficient water can cause the roots of plants to wither.

ZH: 这种花萎缩了，也许需要更多的阳光。
EN: This flower has wilted, perhaps it needs more sunlight.

ZH: 过分修剪会导致树木的枝条萎缩。
EN: Excessive pruning can cause the branches of trees to shrink.

ZH: 这张纸萎缩得很严重，几乎看不清文字了。
EN: This paper has shrunk so much that the text is almost unreadable.

ZH: 长时间暴露在阳光下会导致皮肤萎缩。
EN: Prolonged exposure to sunlight can result in skin atrophy.

ZH: 缺乏运动会导致脂肪细胞的萎缩。
EN: Lack of exercise can cause the shrinkage of fat cells.

ZH: 他的身高明显萎缩了许多。
EN: His height has noticeably shrunk by many.
